This paper is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) category as it focuses on developing a prediction model for software defects. The use of deep learning also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also mentions the use of Abstract Syntax Trees, which suggests that it could belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL) category. Finally, the evaluation of the approach on two datasets suggests that it could belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category.
